S.FORM: Albert II ryax sa tay 14 nqu tay 3, Albert II, squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1958) mrhuw Monaco ta' misuw hya' ga Albert II, aring ryax tay 6 squ byacing tay 4 sa kawas 2005 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. pinqbaqan nya Albert II mqwas biru sa Albert pqwsan biru seneng (Lycée Albert Premier). Albert II, t'aring kawas tay 1979 tehuk kawas tay 1981, mqwas biru sa Bristol pqwsan biru krahu, England. qnxan nya Albert II maki tay kawas 2011 msqun ki Charlene Wittstock, tehuk misuw qani. Jacques, Hereditary Prince of Monaco ga, la'iy ni Albert II. Princess Gabriella, Countess of Carladès ga, la'iy ni Albert II. cinkhulan sa knita' sa brbiru'
